OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1772021938
OL,3,CFirefighters tackle huge blaze at
OL,4,Cderelict church in Southall
OL,6,FDozens of firefighters were deployed
OL,7,Fto a huge fire at a derelict church in
OL,8,FSouthall on Sunday night.
OL,10,FTen fire engines and around 70
OL,11,Ffirefighters where at the scene on
OL,12,FSouth Road, where flames had engulfed
OL,13,Fmost of the ground floor, second floor
OL,14,Fand roof of the building.
OL,16,FCrews used two of the Brigade's 32-
OL,17,Fmetre turntable ladders to help fight
OL,18,Fthe fire from above.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/2
