PN,40502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1772021938
OL,3,CFirefighters tackle huge blaze at
OL,4,Cderelict church in Southall
OL,6,FLondon Fire Brigade said it received
OL,7,Fmore than 20 calls to the area at
OL,8,Faround 9:30pm. The fire was brought
OL,9,Funder control shortly after 12:30am on
OL,10,FMonday morning.
OL,12,FFirefighters remained at the scene on
OL,13,FMonday to fully extinguish the fire
OL,14,Fand the public has been advised to
OL,15,Favoid the area.JSouth Road remains
OL,16,Fclosed in both directions.
OL,18,FThe cause of the fire is being
OL,19,Finvestigated.
